<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id90e1288e-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s7517"><num value="7517">§ 7517.</num><heading> Relationship to other authority</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The authority to provide assistance under this subchapter is in addition to any other authority to provide assistance to the Government of Afghanistan.</p>
